      • getFormRepresentation

        public FormRepresentation getFormRepresentation()
        Returns a FormRepresentation instance which contains the written form of the Sense targeted by this SenseRelation instance.

        Note that this reference is set only if the LexicalEntry containing the targeted Sense does not exist.

        Returns:
        the form representation of the sense targeted by this sense relation or null if the form representation is not set

      • setFormRepresentation

        public void setFormRepresentation(FormRepresentation formRepresentation)
        Sets a FormRepresentation instance which contains the written form of the Sense targeted by this SenseRelation instance.

        Note that this reference should only be set if the LexicalEntry containing the targeted Sense does not exist.

        Parameters:
        formRepresentation - the form representation containing the written form of the sense targeted by this sense relation or null if the form representation is not set
